FBIS4-38115 "drnes124_d_94004" FBIS-NES-94-124 Daily Report 27 Jun 1994 Libya Yemen's Salih Briefs al-Qadhdhafi on Situation Yemen's Salih Briefs al-Qadhdhafi on Situation LD2706211494 Tripoli Libyan Television Network in Arabic 1930 GMT 27 Jun 94 LD2706211494 Tripoli Libyan Television Network Arabic BFN [Text] The brother leader of the revolution [Mu'ammar al-Qadhdhafi] had a telephone conversation today with Yemeni President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, who briefed him on the situation in Yemen and told him of his acceptance of the cease-fire and his readiness to negotiate with the Yemeni Socialist Party.
